g.ns0:text: \\begin{align*}\nP(-a\\leq Z\\leq a) &= P(Z\\leq a)-P(Z<a)\\\\\n &= P(Z\\leq a)-P(Z\\leq -a)\\\\\n &= P(Z\\leq a)-(1-P(Z\\leq a))\\\\\n &= 2P(Z\\leq a)-1=2\\Phi(a)-1\n\\end{align*}
